    {{#code-snippet "html"}}
      <div class="container">
        <!-- content here -->
      </div>
    {{/code-snippet}}

    <p>The alternative is <code>container-fluid</code>. It doesn't
    restrict to any specific width, keeping the whole browser estate
    for your content. You should only use this when building complex
    transactional websites, that need all the browser space available.</p>

    <div class="docs-example">
